These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, march
2 different games are played: chess, scrabble
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Birthday   | march  | april |
| Game       | chess | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | disaster |
| Flower      | poppy     | amaryllis  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, bus
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | woodworking  |
| Transport   | helicopter | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina
2 different pets are kept: mouse, horse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Cigar   | vegafina | prince   |
| Pet       | horse | mouse |

